1.0.name: wordpress/wp-visualpagination
1.0.description:
WP Visual Pagination is an advanced pagination theme framework built on top of the popular WP PageNavi plugin with pre-loaded professionally designed pagination themes. WP Visual pagination allows you create or customize pagination themes for an unlimited number of variations to exactly match the look and feel of your blog. If you need more customization take a look at Visual Pagination Pro.

FEATURES

Create Stunning Pagination Themes

  • Complete control over many aspects of your pagination theme settings
  • Supports CSS based pagination theme designs with unlimited color picking combination
  • Preview theme changes from back-end before you save
  • Powerful pagination theme framework allows for complex pagination designs
  • No HTML Knowledge required – easy to use interface
  • Simpl
